  <answer><![CDATA[<div class="c-page-content">
<p>Canada is suitable for beginner skiers with Whistler being an extremely popular choice. It features slow zones and piste patrol as well as the 'peak to creak' which is the longest blue run from the top of the mountain to the bottom.</p>
